title: july 28: ancient clues to cancer
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the earliest evidence of cancer, from 1.7 million years ago. After, Maia remembers the smash hit “Hey There Delilah” by the Plain White T’s. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
